a:17:{s:4:"name";s:6:"Diarex";s:11:"small_descr";s:140:"The antibacterial and astringent actions of Diarex regularize bowel movements and are effective in the management of diarrhea or dysentery. ";s:14:"small_descr_de";s:123:"Die antibakterielle und adstringierende Wirkung von Diarex reguliert die Stuhlgang und hilft bei Durchfall  und Dysenterie.";s:14:"small_descr_fr";s:151:"Les actions antibactériennes et astringentes de Diarex régularisent les selles et sont efficaces dans le traitement de la diarrhée ou la dysenterie.";s:14:"small_descr_es";s:159:"Los efectos anti-bacterianos y astringentes de Diarex regularizan los movimientos intestinales y son eficaces en el tratamiento de la diarrea o la disentería.";s:14:"small_descr_it";s:138:"L'azione antibatterico e astringente di Diarex regola le evacuazioni di intestino ed è efficace nella direzione di diarrea o dissenteria.";s:10:"full_descr";s:2307:"<p><strong>INDICATIONS </strong></p><p>The antibacterial and astringent actions of Diarex regularize bowel movements and are effective in the management of diarrhea or dysentery. Being an amebicidal agent, Diarex is a beneficial remedy in acute or chronic amebic infections. Diarex's anti-inflammatory and demulcent properties facilitate the healing process of the intestinal mucosa, and its antispasmodic action relieves abdominal colic associated with bowel infection.</p><p><strong>INSTRUCTIONS&nbsp;</strong></p><p>Use <em>Diarex</em> as directed by your doctor.</p><ul><li>Take <em>Diarex</em> by mouth with food.</li><li>Take 2 tablets twice daily, or as directed      by your physician. </li><li>If you miss a dose of <em>Diarex</em> take it as soon as possible. If it is      almost time for your next dose, skip the missed dose and go back to your      regular dosing schedule. Do not take 2 doses at once.</li></ul><p>Ask your health care provider any questions you may have about how to use <em>Diarex</em>.</p><p><strong>STORAGE</strong></p><p>Store <em>Diarex </em>at room temperature away from moisture and sunlight. Keep <em>Diarex </em>out of the reach of children.</p><p><strong>MORE INFO:</strong></p><p><strong>Ingredients:</strong> Kutaja (Holarrhena antidysenterica), &nbsp;Guduchi (Tinospora codifolia), Bilva (Aegle marmelos), Dadima (Punica granatum), Shankh bhasma, Musta (Cyperus rotundus).</p><p><strong>SAFETY INFORMATION</strong></p><p><strong>Do NOT use Diarex if:</strong></p><ul><li>you are allergic to any ingredient in <em>Diarex</em>. &nbsp;</li></ul><p>Some medical conditions may interact with <em>Diarex</em>. Tell your doctor or pharmacist if you have any medical conditions, especially if any of the following apply to you:</p><ul><li>if you are pregnant, planning to become      pregnant, or are breast-feeding</li><li>if you are taking any prescription or      nonprescription medicine, herbal preparation, or dietary supplement</li><li>if you have allergies to medicines, foods,      or other substances.</li></ul><p><strong>Important safety information</strong></p><ul><li>Do not exceed the recommended      dose. </li></ul><p><strong>SIDE EFFECTS</strong></p><p>Diarex is not known to have any side effects if taken as per the prescribed dosage.<br /> <br /></p>";s:13:"full_descr_de";s:0:"";s:13:"full_descr_fr";s:0:"";s:13:"full_descr_es";s:0:"";s:13:"full_descr_it";s:0:"";s:9:"min_price";s:7:"24.8748";s:9:"pack_name";s:7:"bottles";s:4:"type";s:4:"caps";s:7:"analogs";N;s:18:"active_ingredients";N;s:8:"packings";a:1:{i:30;a:10:{i:4773;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"4773";s:5:"count";s:1:"1";s:6:"dosage";d:30;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:5:"32.73";s:4:"name";s:6:"Diarex";}i:4774;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"4774";s:5:"count";s:1:"2";s:6:"dosage";d:30;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:6:"28.366";s:4:"name";s:6:"Diarex";}i:4775;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"4775";s:5:"count";s:1:"3";s:6:"dosage";d:30;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:8:"26.91133";s:4:"name";s:6:"Diarex";}i:4776;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"4776";s:5:"count";s:1:"4";s:6:"dosage";d:30;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:6:"26.184";s:4:"name";s:6:"Diarex";}i:4777;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"4777";s:5:"count";s:1:"5";s:6:"dosage";d:30;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:7:"25.7476";s:4:"name";s:6:"Diarex";}i:4778;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"4778";s:5:"count";s:1:"6";s:6:"dosage";d:30;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:8:"25.45667";s:4:"name";s:6:"Diarex";}i:4779;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"4779";s:5:"count";s:1:"7";s:6:"dosage";d:30;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:8:"25.24886";s:4:"name";s:6:"Diarex";}i:4780;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"4780";s:5:"count";s:1:"8";s:6:"dosage";d:30;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:6:"25.093";s:4:"name";s:6:"Diarex";}i:4781;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"4781";s:5:"count";s:1:"9";s:6:"dosage";d:30;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:8:"24.97178";s:4:"name";s:6:"Diarex";}i:4782;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"4782";s:5:"count";s:2:"10";s:6:"dosage";d:30;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:7:"24.8748";s:4:"name";s:6:"Diarex";}}}}